The following result presents the conditions under which the PDE system (11) and its corresponding ODE system (1) share the same

stability behavior.

Theorem 1. Suppose that u∗ is an equilibrium of (11) independent of x. If u∗ is stable for the flow of (1), then u∗ will be stable for the flow of (11).

